Subject: Re: [T2] where is tdc

Pull both valve covers, roll engine over by hand, when the rocker arms on #3
cylinder are crossing (one opening, one closing) #1 cylinder is at TDC.


Howard

> on a 1978 2.0 FI , is tdc when the intake valve closes completely.
